findings.title: Owner can change tax and liquidity fee
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify tax and liquidity fees.

findings.title: Owner can change maximum transaction amount
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the maximum transaction amount, which could lead to potential security risks.

findings.title: Owner can exclude from the fee
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to exclude certain addresses or users from paying fees.

findings.title: Owner can change minimum tokens before swap
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the minimum tokens required before a swap operation.

findings.title: Owner can change marketing and BUSD charity wallets
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify marketing and BUSD charity wallets without any restrictions.

findings.title: Owner can disable and enable swapAndLiquifyByLimitOnly
findings.description: The owner has privileges to disable and enable swapAndLiquifyByLimitOnly, which could lead to potential security risks.

findings.title: Owner can enable prepareForPreSale and prepareForLaunch presets
findings.description: The owner has privileges to enable prepareForPreSale and prepareForLaunch presets, which could lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner can change router address
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the router address.

findings.title: Owner can change fees
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify fees, which could lead to potential security issues.

findings.title: Owner can lock and unlock
findings.description: The owner has the ability to lock and unlock, which could allow them to retake privileges even after ownership was renounced.

findings.title: Owner can retake privileges even after ownership was renounced
findings.description: The owner can regain control of the contract even after renouncing ownership by using certain functions.
findings.function: lock, unlock, change router address, change fees
